<p itemprop="description">昨天有个好消息，EVA新剧场版电影终于做完了。不过话说，除了电影院其实哪里都能看到EVA（笑）。这次展示的是GT MINI和POP RACE的联名1/64金属车。</p><h2 id="cl_0">购买理由</h2><p itemprop="description">喜欢EVA需要理由吗？帅就可以了。</p><h2 id="cl_1">外观展示</h2><p itemprop="description">简单粗暴直接上图，以下无文字描述。<br/></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5gdggr/pic_2/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202012/18/5fdc36b37a3385652.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" alt="POP RACE有双层包装"/></a>POP RACE有双层包装</span></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5gdggr/pic_3/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/18/5fdc36df4bba48671.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" alt="内层包装有开窗展示设计"/></a>内层包装有开窗展示设计</span></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5gdggr/pic_4/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/18/5fdc374f7ccf91514.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" alt="四个圈"/></a>四个圈</span></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5gdggr/pic_5/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202012/18/5fdc3735a266f7637.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" alt="涂装完美"/></a>涂装完美</span></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5gdggr/pic_6/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/18/5fdc3779b5cab9833.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" alt="引擎盖"/></a>引擎盖</span></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5gdggr/pic_7/' target='_blank'><img alt="新世纪圈钱计划//EVA Racing 1/64" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/18/5fdc379fb08f7440.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5gdggr/pic_8/' target='_blank'><img alt="新世纪圈钱计划//EVA Racing 1/64" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202012/18/5fdc387dc9aed6314.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5gdggr/pic_9/' target='_blank'><img  s